WEBVTT

01:25.370 --> 01:32.000
[Echoes of a Thousand Moons]

01:32.060 --> 01:34.960
[Episode 4]

01:38.840 --> 01:39.910
Brigade Commander

01:40.150 --> 01:41.410
gave a one-word order—

01:41.560 --> 01:42.509
"Die."

01:43.310 --> 01:44.440
Then we die.

01:51.410 --> 01:52.390
Brothers!

01:52.590 --> 01:53.640
Yes!

01:57.620 --> 01:58.840
Move out!

02:26.190 --> 02:35.220
[Command Postof Division Headquarters ]

02:27.240 --> 02:29.800
-Yes.
-Division Commander

02:30.250 --> 02:31.400
I will execute the order immediately.

02:31.400 --> 02:32.600
Division Commander!

02:35.660 --> 02:37.590
Do you know that the 159th Division

02:37.640 --> 02:39.240
has withdrawn from Liu Town?

02:40.300 --> 02:41.490
I just found out.

02:41.700 --> 02:42.660
Why?

02:43.230 --> 02:44.100
Whose order was that?

02:44.100 --> 02:45.910
Who do you think

02:46.470 --> 02:48.140
could bypass the Theater Command,

02:48.140 --> 02:50.270
the Army Group, and the Army Commander

02:50.620 --> 02:51.960
and redeploy an entire division?

02:51.960 --> 02:53.190
The Chairman?

02:56.410 --> 02:57.770
We can retreat too.

02:57.800 --> 02:59.180
We can retreat?

02:59.520 --> 03:00.790
What about the 87th Brigade?

03:00.790 --> 03:02.350
We can't reach them by phone now.

03:02.350 --> 03:03.390
There's no time

03:03.420 --> 03:04.280
to send a messenger.

03:04.280 --> 03:05.340
We should at least dispatch a regiment

03:05.340 --> 03:06.870
to cover their withdrawal.

03:07.570 --> 03:08.720
Since there's no time,

03:08.720 --> 03:10.230
then let them

03:11.880 --> 03:14.880
cover the withdrawal

03:15.190 --> 03:17.450
of the division's main force
and the army at large,

03:17.450 --> 03:19.410
securing the flank and rear.

03:19.520 --> 03:21.270
Division Commander, let me take my men.

03:21.270 --> 03:23.070
Orders from the Army Commander—

03:24.829 --> 03:26.160
withdraw immediately.

04:06.650 --> 04:08.170
Hey, Nishida!

04:08.700 --> 04:10.590
What are you staring at?

04:12.330 --> 04:14.520
This damp air

04:14.550 --> 04:17.100
mixed with wood smoke

04:17.130 --> 04:20.269
smells downright foul.

06:05.950 --> 06:07.750
It feels like someone's coming.

09:36.890 --> 09:37.790
-Freeze!
-Freeze!

09:37.790 --> 09:38.390
Don't!

09:38.390 --> 09:40.090
Don't! Don't! Don't!

09:42.970 --> 09:44.090
Kong Erbao?

09:44.360 --> 09:45.560
Platoon Leader Wang.

09:46.260 --> 09:47.650
What the hell? It's you.

10:02.450 --> 10:03.170
Get up!

10:05.600 --> 10:06.630
What happened?

10:07.080 --> 10:07.870
I...

10:13.330 --> 10:14.970
Erbao, you're back?

10:16.610 --> 10:18.100
I finally found you.

10:18.170 --> 10:20.100
Which direction did you come from?

10:21.840 --> 10:23.470
I... I passed a village.

10:23.720 --> 10:25.050
There is an arch bridge,

10:25.150 --> 10:26.120
covered in corpses.

10:26.120 --> 10:27.480
I crawled over the corpses,

10:27.480 --> 10:28.680
and found you.

10:29.140 --> 10:30.470
The Little Tang bridge?

10:32.120 --> 10:32.900
You got lost?

10:32.930 --> 10:33.680
No.

10:33.870 --> 10:34.910
You said

10:35.000 --> 10:36.510
wherever you go, I follow.

10:36.780 --> 10:38.030
Blindy said I'm lucky.

10:38.030 --> 10:39.290
As long as I follow you,

10:39.390 --> 10:40.720
the bombs won't hit you.

10:41.720 --> 10:43.450
You want to return to the squad?

10:43.590 --> 10:45.990
Wherever the Brigade Commander goes, I go!

10:47.840 --> 10:49.010
Good brother.

10:49.090 --> 10:49.850
Loyal.

10:50.170 --> 10:50.880
I knew it.

10:50.910 --> 10:52.240
You'd never abandon us.

10:53.030 --> 10:53.600
Kong Erbao!

10:53.600 --> 10:54.170
Here!

10:54.500 --> 10:55.000
Rejoin the squad!

10:55.000 --> 10:55.720
Yes, sir!

10:56.550 --> 10:57.360
Move out!

10:59.210 --> 11:01.530
Did you hurt yourself
when you fell just now?

11:01.530 --> 11:02.530
You're loyal.

11:02.560 --> 11:04.490
I knew you were this kind of person.

11:05.320 --> 11:06.200
Good brother.

11:06.300 --> 11:07.070
Good brother.

11:07.070 --> 11:08.080
Let's go.

11:09.080 --> 11:12.210
Fear not the lack of armor,
for my cloak is yours to share.

11:13.920 --> 11:14.740
Not bad.

11:22.680 --> 11:28.750
[Liu Town]

11:42.310 --> 11:43.240
Company Commander Ye!

11:43.240 --> 11:43.550
Yes!

11:43.550 --> 11:45.440
Take two men and scout
the outskirts of the town.

11:45.440 --> 11:46.040
Yes, sir!

11:46.400 --> 11:46.890
Follow me.

11:46.890 --> 11:47.490
Yes, sir.

11:48.740 --> 11:49.170
Platoon Leader Wang!

11:49.170 --> 11:49.810
Yes!

11:49.840 --> 11:50.930
Go check inside the town

11:50.930 --> 11:52.290
and see if there are
any of our allied forces left.

11:52.290 --> 11:53.010
Yes, sir!

11:53.190 --> 11:53.900
Follow me!

11:56.410 --> 11:57.730
Keep a sharp lookout.

12:12.870 --> 12:13.840
What did you find?

12:13.840 --> 12:15.330
The town is completely empty.

12:15.330 --> 12:17.590
There are no allied forces to support us.

12:40.910 --> 12:42.840
The 159th Division has retreated.

12:47.510 --> 12:48.060
How is it?

12:48.200 --> 12:49.240
Brigade Commander,

12:49.240 --> 12:50.600
To the northeast,
we've the spotted the Japanese Army—

12:50.600 --> 12:51.840
infantry and tanks.

12:51.930 --> 12:52.730
Report!

12:54.200 --> 12:54.900
Report!

12:56.720 --> 12:57.360
Brigade Commander,

12:57.360 --> 12:59.490
the road we came from
is full of the Japanese Army.

12:59.490 --> 13:00.520
We can't go back.

13:09.960 --> 13:10.960
If the higher-ups

13:11.480 --> 13:13.270
aren't just ordering
the 159th Division to withdraw,

13:13.270 --> 13:15.030
then we fight the Japanese here!

13:15.030 --> 13:15.690
This way,

13:16.000 --> 13:17.750
we can at least buy more time

13:17.750 --> 13:19.750
for our brothers at home to retreat.

13:20.240 --> 13:21.240
What do you say?

13:21.270 --> 13:22.480
Okay!

13:24.490 --> 13:25.890
When the Japanese fight,

13:25.990 --> 13:28.150
it's always artillery bombardment first,
then tanks charge,

13:28.150 --> 13:29.410
and infantry follows.

13:29.410 --> 13:31.480
So let them in before we strike.

13:31.960 --> 13:32.470
Staff Officer Xie!

13:32.470 --> 13:33.030
Yes!

13:33.120 --> 13:34.240
Take 15 men

13:34.240 --> 13:35.960
and set up defenses
in the western part of the town.

13:35.960 --> 13:36.630
Yes, sir!

13:36.990 --> 13:37.670
Follow me!

13:40.000 --> 13:40.840
Company Commander Ye!

13:40.840 --> 13:41.240
Yes!

13:41.270 --> 13:42.100
Take 10 men

13:42.150 --> 13:43.410
and hide on both sides of the road

13:43.410 --> 13:44.390
to specifically deal with the tanks.

13:44.390 --> 13:44.950
Yes, sir!

13:46.080 --> 13:47.140
Collect grenades!

13:49.940 --> 13:50.660
Ready?

13:51.080 --> 13:51.750
Ready.

13:51.850 --> 13:52.780
Follow me.

13:58.150 --> 13:58.870
Platoon Leader Wang!

13:58.870 --> 13:59.320
Yes!

13:59.370 --> 14:00.550
You're in charge of
cutting off all communication

14:00.550 --> 14:02.120
between the enemy infantry and tanks
from the flank.

14:02.120 --> 14:02.950
Yes, sir!

14:03.100 --> 14:04.020
Follow me!

14:04.370 --> 14:05.600
The rest of you, attention.

14:05.600 --> 14:06.770
Take the machine guns
and occupy the high ground

14:06.770 --> 14:07.900
to set up crossfire.

14:07.910 --> 14:09.620
Do not fire without my order!

14:09.640 --> 14:10.480
Yes, sir!

14:10.920 --> 14:11.920
Go!

15:44.750 --> 15:45.540
Fire!

16:58.290 --> 16:59.530
Ten thousand

17:00.550 --> 17:01.730
heads

17:02.860 --> 17:05.609
must spill

17:17.130 --> 17:18.609
to restore

17:19.880 --> 17:21.440
the world's

17:22.160 --> 17:24.480
balance!

17:48.440 --> 17:49.750
Get ready for artillery!

17:49.750 --> 17:50.440
Go!

17:56.490 --> 17:57.830
Get out of the way!

17:58.120 --> 17:59.610
Move quickly!

17:59.680 --> 18:01.330
Take cover! Quick!

18:01.680 --> 18:02.790
Go!

18:06.500 --> 18:08.190
Take cover! Quick!

18:49.710 --> 18:51.090
This way! Go!

18:50.630 --> 18:52.680
[Blessings]

18:51.120 --> 18:52.160
Go!

18:56.460 --> 18:57.490
Kong Erbao,

18:57.930 --> 18:58.810
come out!

18:59.830 --> 19:00.780
Run!

19:45.310 --> 19:46.440
Brigade Commander!

19:46.850 --> 19:47.980
Brigade Commander!

19:55.030 --> 19:56.350
How many combatants are left?

19:56.350 --> 19:57.400
Brigade Commander,

19:57.400 --> 19:58.400
they are all here.

19:58.510 --> 19:59.400
Gather ammunition.

19:59.400 --> 20:00.920
The Japanese will attack again soon.

20:00.920 --> 20:01.790
Get ready for battle!

20:01.790 --> 20:02.510
Yes, sir!

20:03.030 --> 20:03.720
Gather ammunition!

20:03.720 --> 20:04.920
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

20:12.870 --> 20:14.230
Gas shells!

20:14.260 --> 20:15.720
Cover your mouth and nose!

21:22.820 --> 21:23.620
Huang Ziming.

21:23.910 --> 21:24.670
Yes, sir!

21:24.830 --> 21:26.370
Go gather ammunition, the more the better.

21:26.370 --> 21:27.160
Yes, sir!

21:29.030 --> 21:29.840
Adjutant Zhao.

21:29.840 --> 21:30.560
Yes, sir!

21:32.160 --> 21:33.730
Take my sword and last will,

21:34.070 --> 21:35.250
report the situation here
to Division Commander Sun Huaiyi

21:35.250 --> 21:37.380
at Guangyuan Division Headquarters.

21:39.140 --> 21:39.900
Go quickly.

21:40.180 --> 21:41.420
This is an order!

21:41.440 --> 21:42.840
Yes, Brigade Commander!

21:57.360 --> 21:58.740
Keep formation!

23:17.350 --> 23:18.550
Kill!

23:18.620 --> 23:21.190
Kill!

23:21.790 --> 23:23.750
Kill!

26:15.310 --> 26:16.440
Brigade Commander.

26:17.990 --> 26:19.150
You're still alive.

26:21.030 --> 26:22.020
Yes.

26:22.360 --> 26:24.270
Blindy Huang is dead.

26:28.640 --> 26:30.920
Adjutant Zhao is dead too.

26:33.700 --> 26:35.090
They were all real men.

26:39.020 --> 26:39.900
You are too.

26:42.620 --> 26:44.100
I am not.

26:47.270 --> 26:50.680
They are all dead.

26:53.240 --> 26:54.370
Brigade Commander,

26:54.860 --> 26:55.970
let me carry you.

26:56.640 --> 26:57.570
Let me carry you.

26:58.960 --> 26:59.660
We will

27:00.310 --> 27:01.480
run together.

27:01.750 --> 27:03.240
Erbao.

27:06.840 --> 27:07.950
I have to die here.

27:12.270 --> 27:15.160
What is more important than living?

27:15.300 --> 27:17.100
Take this sword

27:17.590 --> 27:18.750
to Nanjing,

27:19.160 --> 27:21.200
No. 99 Yihe Road,

27:22.070 --> 27:23.640
and give it to my father,

27:24.160 --> 27:25.310
Zhang Ruxian.

27:25.880 --> 27:26.880
Tell him

27:27.090 --> 27:28.880
his son Zhang Yunkui

27:30.530 --> 27:32.210
died loyal to his country.

27:35.920 --> 27:38.120
Repeat what I just said.

27:38.370 --> 27:39.330
Nanjing,

27:39.880 --> 27:40.880
No. 99

27:42.150 --> 27:43.250
Yihe Road,

27:44.810 --> 27:46.130
Zhang Ruxian.

27:46.730 --> 27:47.680
Swear.

27:48.370 --> 27:50.500
I have been an orphan since childhood.

27:51.400 --> 27:52.590
I swear on my wife.

27:53.070 --> 27:54.270
If I can't deliver it,

27:55.310 --> 27:55.960
she

27:56.160 --> 27:57.620
will follow someone else.

28:01.140 --> 28:01.900
Go.

28:04.750 --> 28:08.200
Why do you have to die, Brigade Commander?

28:08.240 --> 28:09.270
Don't cry.

28:11.790 --> 28:12.670
Where is he?

28:13.020 --> 28:13.550
On the right!

28:13.550 --> 28:14.790
I'll cover you.

28:15.700 --> 28:17.060
Run outside the town.

28:17.490 --> 28:19.490
Don't look back, just keep running.

28:19.830 --> 28:21.920
This is an order.

28:23.770 --> 28:24.570
Go!

28:31.850 --> 28:32.740
Erbao,

28:38.680 --> 28:40.610
if you're going to live, live well.

28:42.190 --> 28:43.320
Live unyieldingly.

29:46.440 --> 29:52.960
♪ The wind blows over the hills ♪

29:53.810 --> 29:59.960
♪ Carrying the scent of rice flowers ♪

30:00.930 --> 30:06.580
♪ Moonlight dances on the river ♪

30:07.880 --> 30:13.880
♪ Baby sleeps in peace ♪

30:47.460 --> 30:50.020
♪ Like cloud-veiled moon
the thousand-mile Plain disappears ♪

30:51.000 --> 30:53.680
♪ Like cloud-veiled moon
the thousand-mile Plain disappears ♪

30:54.900 --> 30:57.800
♪ Like cloud-veiled moon
the thousand-mile Plain disappears ♪

30:59.070 --> 31:01.720
♪ Like cloud-veiled moon
the thousand-mile Plain disappears ♪

31:03.810 --> 31:06.530
♪ Wrath sets on end my hair,
I lean on railings ♪

31:07.510 --> 31:10.350
♪ Where I see
the drizzling rain has ceased ♪

31:12.030 --> 31:13.880
♪ Raising my eyes ♪

31:15.040 --> 31:16.890
♪ Towards the skies ♪

31:19.770 --> 31:21.780
♪ I heave long sighs ♪

31:23.630 --> 31:29.960
♪ I heave long sighs ♪

31:31.070 --> 31:37.850
♪ I heave long sighs ♪

32:01.050 --> 32:04.080
♪ To dust is gone the fame
achieved in thirty years ♪

32:05.120 --> 32:07.820
♪ Like cloud-veiled moon
the thousand-mile Plain disappears ♪

32:08.670 --> 32:09.960
♪ Should youthful heads ♪

32:10.550 --> 32:14.780
♪ In vain turn grey ♪

32:16.490 --> 32:19.390
♪ We would regret for aye ♪

32:20.190 --> 32:23.160
♪ We would regret for aye ♪

32:24.140 --> 32:26.910
♪ We would regret for aye ♪

32:27.880 --> 32:31.190
♪ We would regret for aye ♪

32:31.580 --> 32:34.690
♪ Lost our capitals,
What a burning shame! ♪

32:35.370 --> 32:38.590
♪ Lost our capitals,
What a burning shame! ♪

32:39.490 --> 32:40.830
♪ Driving our chariots of war ♪

32:41.490 --> 32:45.810
♪ we'd go
To break through our relentless foe ♪

32:47.120 --> 32:49.970
♪ Valiantly we'd cut off each head ♪

32:50.700 --> 32:53.510
♪ Laughing, we'd drink
the blood they shed. ♪

32:54.430 --> 32:56.570
♪ When we've reconquered ♪

32:57.310 --> 32:58.050
♪ When we've reconquered ♪

32:58.530 --> 32:59.420
♪ When we've reconquered ♪

33:00.460 --> 33:03.540
♪ our lost land ♪

33:04.130 --> 33:06.180
♪ In triumph would return our army grand ♪

33:06.930 --> 33:09.050
♪ In triumph would return our army grand ♪

33:09.910 --> 33:11.070
♪ In triumph would return our army grand ♪

33:11.710 --> 33:14.740
♪ To dust is gone the fame
achieved in thirty years ♪

33:15.780 --> 33:18.590
♪ Like cloud-veiled moon
the thousand-mile Plain disappears ♪

33:19.420 --> 33:20.820
♪ Should youthful heads ♪

33:21.560 --> 33:25.300
♪ In vain turn grey ♪

33:26.190 --> 33:31.400
♪ We would regret for aye ♪

33:34.600 --> 33:35.680
Yueming,

33:35.830 --> 33:37.310
you will surely shed tears
for the sacrifices

33:37.310 --> 33:39.840
the Chinese people made in the battle,

33:39.940 --> 33:43.460
but Mom must tell you the true history.

33:44.610 --> 33:46.120
Their sacrifices

33:46.150 --> 33:48.620
did not reverse the passivity of the war.

33:48.830 --> 33:50.000
Due to the Nationalist Government's

33:50.000 --> 33:52.200
fatal flaws at the strategic level

33:52.200 --> 33:54.720
and the extreme chaos
in the command system,

33:55.060 --> 33:58.540
such sacrifices occurred again and again.

33:59.240 --> 34:01.620
Although they inflicted real resistance

34:01.650 --> 34:03.270
and significant losses
on the Japanese Army,

34:03.270 --> 34:06.320
in the end, we still lost Shanghai.

34:07.000 --> 34:08.960
It would take many years before I

34:08.960 --> 34:12.030
could understand
the true nature of this war,

34:12.030 --> 34:15.139
before she could understand why we lost

34:15.170 --> 34:18.290
and how we might have won.

34:18.440 --> 34:19.190
Hello.

34:19.540 --> 34:20.580
Excuse me,

34:20.960 --> 34:22.030
where is this place?

34:22.030 --> 34:23.320
We don't know either.

34:24.280 --> 34:25.080
Thank you.

34:48.360 --> 34:49.150
Sir.

34:49.360 --> 34:50.360
Excuse me,

34:51.510 --> 34:52.280
do you know

34:52.510 --> 34:53.489
where this is?

34:53.760 --> 34:55.190
This is Wuxi.

34:55.320 --> 34:56.280
Wuxi?

34:58.360 --> 35:01.590
Then do you know how to get to Wuhan?

35:01.820 --> 35:02.740
Wuhan?

35:03.950 --> 35:04.770
Go that way.

35:05.440 --> 35:07.070
That way leads to Taicang Port.

35:07.070 --> 35:08.550
There are ships to Wuhan.

35:10.240 --> 35:11.470
What about Nanjing?

35:11.580 --> 35:12.270
Nanjing?

35:12.800 --> 35:13.700
Go this way.

35:13.960 --> 35:17.420
Heading to the train station
is the direction toward Nanjing.

35:21.510 --> 35:23.570
Little brother, you must be thirsty.

35:24.230 --> 35:25.230
Drink some water.

35:27.880 --> 35:29.960
Thank you.

35:36.030 --> 35:37.590
Thank you.

35:37.610 --> 35:38.690
Thank you, sir.

36:01.760 --> 36:03.200
Liu Town.

36:04.040 --> 36:05.770
Which direction is Liu Town?

36:06.920 --> 36:08.980
The Brigade Commander is in Liu Town.

36:21.100 --> 36:22.230
Brigade Commander.

36:22.710 --> 36:23.460
Well,

36:23.590 --> 36:24.110
Nan...

36:25.320 --> 36:27.140
I have to go to Nanjing,

36:27.960 --> 36:28.920
but

36:30.510 --> 36:32.930
I definitely need to go to Wuhan first.

36:33.110 --> 36:35.140
I have to find Xiaoyue first.

36:35.320 --> 36:36.580
Then I'll go to Nanjing

36:36.710 --> 36:39.590
to deliver the sword
to your father, okay?

36:41.790 --> 36:42.590
Don't worry.

36:45.220 --> 36:47.020
I will definitely go to Nanjing.

37:20.670 --> 37:21.360
Wait,

37:22.070 --> 37:23.200
Brigade Commander,

37:23.220 --> 37:24.820
are you really following me?

37:24.950 --> 37:25.790
I...

37:27.110 --> 37:29.300
I'm just a lowly worm.

37:29.440 --> 37:31.000
Please, spare me!

37:31.020 --> 37:31.620
I...

37:32.110 --> 37:34.030
I have to go to Wuhan.

38:09.580 --> 38:13.010
[Nanjing]

38:12.970 --> 38:14.110
Great-grandfather!

38:14.110 --> 38:15.070
Madam!

38:16.560 --> 38:17.670
Great-grandfather!

38:17.670 --> 38:18.670
Any new battle reports?

38:18.670 --> 38:20.280
No new reports yet.

38:20.670 --> 38:23.320
I saw Deputy Division Commander Liao
on the way.

38:23.320 --> 38:25.180
Liao Fengnian is back in Nanjing?

38:26.110 --> 38:26.880
Father,

38:27.230 --> 38:29.160
does that mean Yunkui is also back?

38:32.590 --> 38:33.680
I'll go ask him.

38:34.360 --> 38:35.190
Get my clothes.

38:35.190 --> 38:35.880
Yes.

38:48.630 --> 38:49.550
Mrs. Liu,

38:50.320 --> 38:51.770
Liao Fengnian is back in Nanjing.

38:51.770 --> 38:53.430
Yunkui should be back too.

38:53.590 --> 38:55.390
The young master is coming back?

38:55.590 --> 38:56.590
That's great.

38:57.110 --> 38:59.640
Just in time for some
duck blood vermicelli soup.

38:59.640 --> 39:01.080
Is it the batch I made?

39:02.550 --> 39:03.980
Who else would it be?

39:04.190 --> 39:05.320
Look at the noodles—

39:05.440 --> 39:06.640
some are thick,

39:07.000 --> 39:08.510
some are thin, all crooked.

39:08.510 --> 39:09.480
It's so ugly.

39:10.070 --> 39:11.340
It looks fine to me.

39:11.360 --> 39:12.320
Let me do it.

39:13.150 --> 39:14.190
Be careful.

39:15.210 --> 39:20.800
[Nationalist Government]

39:33.670 --> 39:37.330
[Nationalist Government]

40:08.200 --> 40:14.550
[Nationalist Government]

40:08.880 --> 40:11.400
The Nationalist Government.

40:11.440 --> 40:12.510
So big.

40:14.620 --> 40:17.800
[[Zhang's Mansion]]

40:17.840 --> 40:23.500
[[Understanding Water, Honoring Mountain]]

40:30.930 --> 40:33.400
[No. 99, Yihe Road]

40:35.830 --> 40:36.710
Madam,

40:36.840 --> 40:37.900
I have to say,

40:38.000 --> 40:39.000
your hands

40:39.020 --> 40:41.030
are meant for embroidery and writing.

40:41.030 --> 40:43.210
I should be the one doing this.

40:45.440 --> 40:46.510
Sour liquid.

40:46.540 --> 40:47.550
How many times have I told you?

40:47.550 --> 40:48.800
You just can't remember.

40:48.800 --> 40:49.510
The jar failed—starch didn't settle.

40:49.510 --> 40:51.110
Look, it's all sticking together.

40:51.110 --> 40:52.320
Just pull it apart.

40:52.320 --> 40:53.760
I think it's fine.

40:54.360 --> 40:56.690
You should listen to the elders.

40:56.880 --> 40:58.840
This is the method
my grandmother taught me.

40:58.840 --> 41:00.840
Once it goes in the pot,
it'll all stick together

41:00.840 --> 41:01.510
in a lump.

41:01.550 --> 41:03.750
Won't it separate when you boil it?

41:03.880 --> 41:04.880
Besides,

41:04.960 --> 41:07.110
it doesn't matter if you like it or not.

41:07.150 --> 41:08.610
As long as Yunkui likes it.

41:10.760 --> 41:11.800
You're asking for trouble!

41:11.800 --> 41:12.550
Who let you in?

41:12.550 --> 41:14.290
Quick, quick, get out!

41:14.710 --> 41:15.440
Mrs. Liu,

41:17.510 --> 41:18.920
are there any potstickers left?

41:18.920 --> 41:19.670
Yes.

41:20.000 --> 41:20.730
Go pack some.

41:23.840 --> 41:24.480
Wait outside.

41:24.480 --> 41:25.750
I'll get them for you.

41:25.960 --> 41:27.280
I'm not a beggar.

41:31.510 --> 41:32.590
What are you doing?

41:36.710 --> 41:39.970
I'm here to deliver a message
for Brigade Commander Zhang.

41:44.460 --> 41:46.150
The 87th Brigade?

41:46.360 --> 41:47.160
Yes.

41:47.210 --> 41:48.670
I'm from the 87th Brigade.

41:48.960 --> 41:50.420
Our young master is
your Brigade Commander.

41:50.420 --> 41:51.940
This is his wife.

41:53.680 --> 41:54.630
Madam.

42:01.400 --> 42:01.970
You...

42:02.920 --> 42:03.710
You came...

42:06.960 --> 42:08.000
Where is Yunkui?

42:09.170 --> 42:10.440
Isn't he back?

42:15.110 --> 42:16.640
Is Old Master Zhang at home?

42:16.920 --> 42:18.250
Our Brigade Commander ordered

42:18.250 --> 42:20.380
that I can only speak to the Old Master.

42:25.840 --> 42:26.760
He went out.

42:26.780 --> 42:28.190
You can tell me, it's okay.

42:28.190 --> 42:29.440
Yes, it's okay.

42:29.550 --> 42:30.380
No.

42:30.670 --> 42:31.540
It's an order.

42:31.960 --> 42:33.820
I can only speak to the Old Master.

42:35.750 --> 42:36.830
Okay.

42:39.230 --> 42:40.070
Mrs. Liu,

42:40.280 --> 42:41.480
go make some hot food.

42:42.960 --> 42:43.800
Wait a moment.

42:43.840 --> 42:44.920
Duck blood vermicelli soup.

42:44.920 --> 42:46.030
Okay, got it.

42:49.710 --> 42:50.630
Young man,

42:50.960 --> 42:52.230
don't stand outside.

42:52.440 --> 42:53.440
Come in and rest.

42:53.460 --> 42:54.500
Follow me.

42:55.770 --> 42:56.640
Madam.,

42:57.030 --> 42:58.570
I won't go in.

42:58.630 --> 42:59.500
I...

43:00.510 --> 43:02.000
I'll just wait in the courtyard.
